title: Glenn Beck FOX NEWS 04.13.09 || GREENDEVIL
description:
Glenn Beck's FOX TV Show, originally aired April 13th, 2009.

DivX 6.8.5 Codec (8 Logical CPUs) 1-pass, MP3 128k. Obviously not HD (Maybe someday?)

~ Green Devil

SIDE NOTE: Glenn handled the "pass-out" situation really well, and I believe his quick reaction, as well as words coming out of the break, are indicative of the good-hearted character he embodies. You may not like his politics, but give the guy a break once in a while. 

You can find that at time index 10:55, as I know some of you are only downloading it just because of that.
